track_notes: There is no parking allowed at the track start. Suggest you park nearer to the MA-2200 in one of the estate roads or walk from the town. I undertook this walk on my way back from the Siller Pass walk from Cala Vicenc to Port de Pollenca. This was a challenging scramble in parts, so I recommend the route only for sure footed confident agile fell walkers.  Overgrown a little for the first 10m then a case of reading the ground above you and carefully picking your way between boulders and vegetation.  I found it easier coming down than I thought it would be. Fantastic vista from the summit. If you have a full day to spare you could pair this with MA-057. I will also input my down route - not much to choose between them.
track_title: Up track starts at end of tarmac road by house

track_notes: My down track from MA-046 Talaia Vella - 25th April 2015. Includes the walk back to The Romantic Hotel in Port de Pollenca.
